From 58bd3d484ea2e0ab1bcb18d12828fb0cb8e0dc38 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <claude@anthropic.com>
Date: Wed, 22 Apr 2026 18:58:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Tier 1 quick wins: scoped message fetch, toast errors,
 cleanup

- Messages.jsx: Replace global Message.list(500) + client-side filter with
  Message.filter({ thread_id }). Fixes largest perf issue and metadata leak.
- Messages.jsx + ServiceRequests.jsx: Replace browser alert() with sonner
  toast.error() for all user-facing error surfaces (7 sites).
- Delete src/components/ProtectedRoute.jsx: unused and referenced
  undefined context properties (authChecked, checkUserAuth).
- eslint.config.js: Enable react-hooks/exhaustive-deps as warning to
  surface stale-closure bugs in subscription effects.
---
 eslint.config.js                  |  1 +
 src/components/ProtectedRoute.jsx | 37 -------------------------------
 src/pages/Messages.jsx            | 18 ++++++++++-----
 src/pages/ServiceRequests.jsx     |  9 ++++----
 4 files changed, 19 insertions(+), 46 deletions(-)
 delete mode 100644 src/components/ProtectedRoute.jsx

